## ğŸš€ **HOW TO USE THIS PROJECT:**

### **1. Create the folder structure:**
```bash
mkdir FoodRecipe
cd FoodRecipe
mkdir -p src/{navigation,screens,components,data,utils,redux} assets
```

### **2. Copy all files into their respective folders**

### **3. Install dependencies:**
```bash
npm install
```

### **4. Run the app:**
```bash
npx expo start
```

### **5. For Expo Snack:**
- Go to [snack.expo.dev](https://snack.expo.dev)
- Create the same flat file structure (Snack doesn't support nested folders)
- Copy the content of each file
- Run the app

